OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHotels battle to beat      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbedbugs as outbreaks rise  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, "A fortnight ago we had a detection of 
OL,6, a bedbug and it's frightening," says   
OL,7, Max Malka, owner of the Montlhery Paris
OL,8, Sud Hotel, 15km south of Paris.        
OL,10,FYou don't know if bugs are moving      
OL,11,Fbetween rooms, he said, and you risk   
OL,12,Fbeing sued if a guest is bitten badly. 
OL,14,FHis is one of many firms seeking       
OL,15,Fsolutions amid a rise in reported      
OL,16,Foutbreaks in France and the UK.        
OL,18,FAnd firms are turning to tech - both   
OL,19,Fold and new - to catch outbreaks early,
OL,20,Fwhich is vital to stopping the spread. 
